  + DERIVATION:
    Derived from NPT Cognitive Participation 2.4 Activation as stated in the companion journal article.
    Tier: Architecture.  Coordination: High (governed infrastructure).
    Implementation-mode link: this pattern separates absorbed input from multiplied input.
    The paper names the structural principle (collective-choice, governance-follows-contribution) and operationalises it via steering group, contribution log, and stewarded coordinator role.
